title: Meet Matt Stonie, the world's number-one competitive eater
text: The Filter Meet Matt Stonie, the world's number-one competitive eater He can consume 62 hot dogs in just 10 minutes, yet this 23-year old weighs nine stone, is studying to be a dietician and considers extreme eating a 'science' Matt 'Megatoad' Stonie consuming 182 rashers of bacon in 5 minutes Photo: Getty
